title: Newly Renovated 3 Bedroom/3 Bath With Panoramic Views !!!!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-Certified 100% sprinklered apartments', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
